    <note>Lu(9) E [16384] I am identifying this first generation of Huating county (modern Songjiang, Shanghai, etc.) Lu with radical 149 as generational indicator (same as Lu(9) Hui [7053], whose lineage moved from Beijing area to Luoyang, and who is designated as a member of a different lineage) as cousins. The next generation of Lu(9), Quan [16387] and Kui [16388] were Huating men registered as Kaifeng residents, and are identified as E's nephews, and Yirou [16329], also a Huating Lu(9) registered in Kaifeng, as Quan's nephew. I am moving the lineage to Kaifeng with Quan, although the move probably took place with the radical 149 generation. Yunjian zhi, 'zhong,' 35a.</note>
